uote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>He also brought up Carrie Fisher\'s appearance in the new Star Wars as an example of a way this posthumous CGI work can be done well, apparently missing the difference between honoring Fisher\'s legacy in a role she was already scheduled to play and plopping James Dean in some random war movie half a century after his death.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:quote {\"quoteStyle\":\"td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"} -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"><p>When discussing whether resurrecting Dean digitally crosses a line with regards to posthumous casting, Ernst explained, \"Anyone that is brought back to life - you have to respect them.\" He noted Fisher\'s posthumous appearances in the Star Wars franchise, saying that if the actress had expressed never wanting to be in a film after her death, or if her legacy or that of the franchise could be \"tarnished\" because of her casting, \"then that should be a line.\"</p></blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:quote {\"quoteStyle\":\"td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"} -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote td_pull_quote td_pull_center\"><p>\"I think the line should be ... you must always honor the deceased\'s wishes and try to act in a way that is honorable and full of dignity,\" Ernst said.</p></blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>Again, this is extremely different, since Dean could never have stated he didn\'t want to appear in a film after his death because, uh, how would he have imagined that was even a possibility-but whatever. Finding Jack is still headed into production with an expected release on November 11, 2020, whether we like it or not.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Noel Gallagher says Liam\'s tweets are the reason Oasis won\'t reunite', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'noel-gallagher-says-liams-tweets-are-the-reason-oasis-wont-reunite', '', '', '2024-08-07 08:20:42', '2024-08-07 08:20:42', '', 0, 'http://tdi_4_26b', 0, 'post', '', 0),
